r%20of%20the%20House%20on%20Mosfilmovskaya%20residential%20complex%20in%202016.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f96899b3045b292f636be9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20House%20on%20Mosfilmovskaya%20complex%2C%20or%20Mosfilm%20tower%2C%20is%20located%20in%20one%20of%20Moscow's%20upscale%20neighborhoods.%3Cp%3ESergei%20Karpukhin%2FREUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20upscale%20residential%20tower%20near%20Moscow's%20city%20center%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20drone%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20one%20of%20Ukraine's%20deepest%20strikes%20into%20Moscow%2C%20which%20is%20preparing%20for%20its%20Victory%20Day%20parade.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine%20often%20launches%20such%20strikes%20to%20undermine%20the%20parade%2C%20which%20won't%20be%20displaying%20equipment%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Ukrainian%20drone%20hit%20a%20luxury%20high-rise%20tower%20in%20Moscow%20on%20Monday%2C%20a%20rare%20attack%20near%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Russian%20capital%20just%20days%20before%20this%20year's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvladimir-putin-bodyguard-interceptor-drone-victory-day-parade-video-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVictory%20Day%20parade%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20videos%20posted%20on%20Russian%20Telegram%20news%20channels%20appear%20to%20show%20debris%20strewn%20across%20a%20main%20road%20near%20the%20Mosfilm%20tower%2C%20a%20two-building%20residential%20complex%20about%204%20miles%20from%20Moscow's%20city%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20was%20unable%20to%20determine%20when%20these%20videos%20and%20photos%20were%20taken%2C%20but%20they%20are%20consistent%20with%20street%20markings%20and%20the%20city%20layout%20near%20the%20Mosfilm%20tower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20clip%20showed%20emergency%20vehicles%20and%20halted%20road%20traffic%20at%20a%20junction%20next%20to%20the%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20taller%20of%20the%20two%20buildings%20appears%20to%20have%20been%20the%20target%2C%20with%20photos%20showing%20visible%20damage%20to%20one%20of%20the%2054-floor%20tower's%20upper%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoscow's%20mayor%2C%20Sergei%20Sobyanin%2C%20confirmed%20an%20attack%20on%20Monday%20evening%2C%20saying%20that%20a%20drone%20had%20struck%20a%20building%20on%20Mosfilmovskaya%20Street.%20Sobyanin%20said%20that%20there%20were%20no%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonday's%20attack%20on%20the%20Mosfilm%20tower%20is%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-drones-hit-deep-in-russia-security-source-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUkraine's%20deepest%20drone%20hits%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20heavily%20defended%20Russian%20capital.%20The%20skyscraper%20is%20located%20in%20one%20of%20Moscow's%20most%20affluent%20neighborhoods%2C%20with%20major%20foreign%20embassies%20down%20the%20road%20and%20a%20nearby%20city-center%20golf%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20also%20comes%20five%20days%20before%20Russia%20is%20set%20to%20hold%20its%20annual%20parade%20celebrating%20the%20Soviet%20Union's%20victory%20over%20Nazi%20Germany%20during%20World%20War%20II.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20Ukraine%20has%20harassed%20Moscow%20with%20attempted%20drone%20attacks%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20parade%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20grandest%20displays%20of%20Russia's%20military%20might.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Moscow%20prepared%20last%20year%20to%20host%20dozens%20of%20world%20leaders%20for%20one%20of%20its%20highest-profile%20editions%20of%20the%20parade%2C%20Kyiv%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F60000-passengers-stuck-russian-airports-tourism-association-drone-strikes-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erepeatedly%20disrupted%20local%20airports%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20launching%20waves%20of%20drone%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20Kremlin%20said%20it%20would%20hold%20a%20scaled-down%20version%20of%20the%20parade%2C%20with%20no%20displays%20of%20significant%20military%20equipment%20due%20to%20the%20war%20situation%20and%20the%20threat%20of%20Ukrainian%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20telling%2C%26quot%3B%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20on%20Monday%20while%20attending%20a%20summit%20in%20Armenia.%20%26quot%3BIt%20shows%20they%20are%20not%20strong%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelenskyy%20hinted%20at%20further%20drone%20threats%20on%20Moscow%20this%20month%2C%20saying%20that%20Russian%20officials%20%26quot%3Bfear%20drones%20may%20buzz%20over%20Red%20Square%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20parade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Russian%20defense%20ministry%20said%20that%20it%20had%20shot%20down%20at%20least%20117%20Ukrainian%20drones%20bound%20for%20the%20capital%20on%20Sunday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Moscow%20about%20275%20miles%20from%20the%20nearest%20Ukrainian%20border%2C%20Kyiv%20often%20uses%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drone-defense-tech-industry-warfare-russia-attacks-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efixed-wing%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20attack%20the%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-drone-strikes-moscow-skyscraper-mosfilm-threatens-victory-day-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777954802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f96ac6405e0cf89dc87041%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukrainian-drone-strikes-moscow-skyscraper-mosfilm-threatens-victory-day-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20is%20hosting%20a%20scaled-down%20version%20of%20the%20parade%20this%20year%2C%20saying%20it%20won't%20display%20military%20equipment%20due%20to%20the%20war%20situation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh)%22%2C%22enga