i%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20does%20commissions%20of%20famous%20cities%20and%20places%2C%20painted%20on%20boarding%20passes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20said%20turning%20her%20hobby%20into%20her%20job%20has%20been%20fulfilling%20and%20helped%20her%20unlearn%20the%20corporate%20mindset.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Victoria%20Hugo%2C%20a%2028-year-old%20art%20business%20owner%20based%20in%20Surrey%2C%20UK.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20decade%20as%20a%20content%20creator%20and%20running%20a%20social%20media%20business%2C%20I%20quit%20to%20start%20painting%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2017%2C%20I%20made%20a%20TikTok%20account%20posting%20videos%20about%20body%20painting%2C%20face%20painting%2C%20and%20canvas%20work.%20My%20channel%20grew%20quickly%2C%20and%20within%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20year%2C%20I%20had%20a%20million%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20brands%20weren't%20on%20the%20platform%20yet%2C%20and%20I%20could%20help%20them%20get%20on%20it.%20So%20in%202021%2C%20I%20started%20a%20TikTok%20agency%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewith%20two%20cofounders%2C%20working%20with%20clients%20across%20different%20sectors%2C%20from%20hospitality%20to%20beauty.%20By%20the%20time%20I%20left%20last%20year%2C%20we%20were%20turning%20over%20about%20%C2%A3500%2C000%2C%20or%20about%20%24675%2C000%2C%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20loved%20the%20challenge%20and%20the%20variety%20that%20the%20job%20brought%20me%2C%20but%20it%20left%20me%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-quit-kpmg-singapore-india-pursue-poetry-creative-writing-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eno%20time%20for%20my%20art%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%20an%20all-or-nothing%20person%2C%20so%20if%20I%20could%20only%20give%20my%20art%205%25%20of%20my%20time%2C%20it%20wasn't%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20nearly%2010%20years%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclipping-social-media-tiktok-viral-band-geese-advertising-authentic-fake-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eon%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20sure%20if%20this%20is%20really%20fulfilling%20me%20in%20the%20happiness%20department.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20I%20exited%20the%20business%20last%20year%20to%20paint%20full%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f74b1b78-5fda-4520-9113-81bc358b1122%5C%22%3EAir%20ticket%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hugo's%20business%20started%20with%20a%20painting%20of%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%20on%20an%20Air%20India%20boarding%20pass.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e9ed953fecbb42897a311a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223213%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHugo's%20business%20started%20with%20a%20painting%20of%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%20on%20an%20Air%20India%20boarding%20pass.%3Cp%3EVictoria%20Hugo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20my%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehusband%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20I%20took%20what%20we%20called%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frarely-travel-with-husband-better-for-marriage-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehoney%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20after%20we%20got%20married%20and%20traveled%20to%20places%20we'd%20always%20wanted%20to%20go.%20I'm%20a%20raging%20ticket%20hoarder%20%E2%80%94%20boarding%20passes%2C%20little%20mementos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20one%20trip%20in%20October%2C%20I%20had%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-india-business-class-long-flight-review-newark-new-delhi-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAir%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20boarding%20passes%2C%20and%20I%20remember%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20could%20just%20paint%20a%20moment%20from%20these%20trips%20on%20a%20boarding%20pass.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20it%20was%20just%20for%20me.%20I%20didn't%20think%20people%20would%20buy%20them.%20I%20painted%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-visiting-india-for-first-time-with-family-kids-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETaj%20Mahal%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20one%20of%20the%20passes%2C%20for%20a%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20have%20all%20my%20old%20boarding%20passes%2C%20so%20I%20asked%20a%20graphic%20designer%20friend%20to%20create%20editable%20versions%20I%20could%20paint%20on.%20Then%20I%20painted%20more%20from%20my%20trips%20and%20posted%20them%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20friend%20commissioned%20one%20for%20her%20husband%2C%20and%20then%20I%20posted%20a%20video%20in%20January.%20Within%20a%20day%2C%20it%20exploded.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20had%20so%20many%20DMs%20asking%20how%20to%20buy%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year%2C%20I've%20gone%20all%20in%20on%20this.%20I've%20received%20about%2060%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20painting%20itself%20takes%20between%20two%20and%2010%20hours%2C%20depending%20on%20its%20complexity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hugo%20paints%20famous%20cities%20on%20boarding%20passes.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e9ed1e367066d7c2970008%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHugo%20paints%20famous%20cities%20on%20boarding%20passes.%3Cp%3EVictoria%20Hugo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20want%20it%20framed%2C%20I%20mount%20and%20frame%20it%20before%20shipping%20it%20off.%20Overall%2C%20each%20piece%20usually%20takes%20between%20one%20and%20three%20days%20from%20start%20to%20finish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20received%20a%20wedding%20order%20of%2013%20boarding%20pass%20paintings%20of%20places%20that%20were%20important%20to%20the%20couple.%20They%20didn't%20have%20table%20numbers%3B%20rather%2C%20they%20had%20the%20%26quot%3BLondon%20table%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSeoul%20table%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20so%20forth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20scanned%20those%20designs%20and%20created%20100%20individual%20boarding%20passes%20for%20the%20guests%2C%20each%20with%20their%20name%20and%20table%20assignment.%20I%20cut%20them%20all%20out%20individually.%20It%20was%20a%20long%20day%2C%20but%20it%20turned%20out%20great.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de0b85e2-460f-4d88-a5b6-1943aaa11f62%5C%22%3EThe%20risk%20is%20paying%20off%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hugo%20painting%20on%20a%20boarding%20pass.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e9ee62367066d7c297000c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHugo%20said%20the%20business%20is%20proving%20profitable.%3Cp%3EVictoria%20Hugo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20charge%20%C2%A3195%20for%20an%20unframed%20piece%20and%20%C2%A3245%20for%20a%20framed%20piece%2C%20plus%20shipping.%20I've%20also%20added%20a%20fast-track%20option%20for%20people%20who%20leave%20things%20to%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20so%20they%20can%20pay%20%C2%A3100%20and%20guarantee%20their%20painting%20will%20be%20completed%20within%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20one%20costs%20me%20roughly%20%C2%A350%20to%20produce%20if%20it's%20framed%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20is%20just%20time%20and%20labor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20first%20few%20months%2C%20it%20made%20more%20money%20than%20I%20earned%20in%20salary%20at%20the%20social%20media%20agency.%20I'm%20very%20confident%20I%20won't%20need%20a%20second%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20a%20few%20inquiries%20about%20events%20and%20wedding%20packages%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20the%20big%20money%20comes%20from%20compared%20to%20the%20one-off%20commissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFunnily%20enough%2C%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20has%20been%20the%20mental%20block%20of%20not%20being%20confident%20that%20I've%20created%20something%20that's%20valuable%20to%20the%20customer.%20I've%20just%20fallen%20into%20it%2C%20and%20it's%20happened%20really%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225150ae9b-8b09-4a2e-924f-1e82a5b317a5%5C%22%3EUnlearning%20the%20mindset%20of%20chasing%20milestones%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%2C%20I%20was%20always%20chasing%20milestones%2C%20like%20getting%20verified%20or%20hitting%20a%20million%20followers%20on%20TikTok.%20In%20my%20business%2C%20the%20aim%20was%20to%20make%20it%20profitable.%20But%20with%20this%2C%20I%20have%20a%20completely%20different%20mindset%2C%20which%20I%20need%20right%20now%20as%20I'm%20pregnant%20with%20my%20first%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20that%20I%20have%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscuro-art-studio-singapore-business-advice-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eflexibility%20to%20paint%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20plan%2C%20edit%2C%20or%20do%20admin%20jobs%2C%20and%20that%20I%20can%20take%20my%20foot%20off%20the%20gas%20and%20enjoy%20what%20I'm%20doing.%20I%20want%20to%20do%20it%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20enjoy%20it%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20see%20where%20it%20can%20go%2C%20like%20working%20with%20brands%20like%20tourism%20boards%20or%20airlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20get%20to%20do%20my%20hobby%20for%20a%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20thought%20they%20were%20kidding.%20Now%2C%20I%20get%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-left-business-paint-full-time-air-tickets-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777953661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69e9beff367066d7c296ffac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-left-business-paint-full-time-air-tickets-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Victoria%20Hugo%20left%20her%20social%20media%20business%20to%20start%20an%20art%20hustle%2C%20doing%20commissions%20of%20famous%20cities%20and