essinsider.com%2Fai-startup-founders-warning-elad-gilsell-while-boom-lasts-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20outlining%20long-term%20financial%20targets%20and%20early%20signs%20of%20traction%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20meeting%20with%20analysts%2C%20ServiceNow%20President%20and%20CFO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fservicenow-ceo-bill-mc-dermott-ai-reorienting-global-economy-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGina%20Mastantuono%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20the%20company%20is%20targeting%20more%20than%20%2430%20billion%20in%20subscription%20revenue%20by%202030%2C%20up%20from%20an%20expected%20%2415.7%20billion%20in%202026.%20There's%20potential%20upside%20to%20more%20than%20%2432%20billion%2C%20implying%20a%20roughly%2020%25%20compound%20annual%20growth%20rate%2C%20the%20CFO%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EServiceNow%20also%20pushed%20back%20on%20concerns%20that%20AI%20could%20erode%20profit%20margins.%20The%20company%20said%20AI%20reasoning%20accounts%20for%20less%20than%2010%25%20of%20its%20cost%20to%20serve%2C%20helping%20it%20maintain%20gross%20margins%20above%2080%25%20even%20as%20AI%20usage%20rises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMastantuono%20also%20forecast%20operating%20margin%20and%20free%20cash%20flow%20margin%20expansion%20of%20100%20basis%20points%20in%202027.%20By%202030%2C%20ServiceNow%20aims%20to%20reach%20a%20%26quot%3BRule%20of%2060%2B%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20high%20bar%20that%20combines%20revenue%20growth%20and%20free%20cash%20flow%20margins%20that%20total%2060%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20many%20software%20stocks%20have%20plunged%20in%20the%20past%20year%20on%20concern%20that%20generative%20AI%20tools%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-ate-world-now-ai-eating-software-saas-anthropic-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereduce%20demand%20for%20software%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20help%20customers%20create%20their%20own%20software%20to%20replace%20traditional%20offerings.%20The%20new%20forecasts%20from%20ServiceNow%20are%20aimed%20at%20reassuring%20investors%20that%20AI%20is%20not%20a%20threat%20to%20its%20business%20and%20could%20instead%20become%20a%20major%20growth%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20update%20comes%20after%20a%20solid%20first%20quarter%20from%20ServiceNow%20in%20which%20subscription%20revenue%20rose%2022%25%20year%20over%20year%20to%20%243.67%20billion.%20Still%2C%20the%20stock%20fell%20following%20that%20earnings%20report%20on%20concerns%20about%20AI's%20impact%2C%20margins%2C%20and%20deal%20delays%20due%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20central%20piece%20of%20ServiceNow's%20new%20pitch%20is%20AI%20monetization.%20On%20Monday%2C%20the%20CFO%20said%20its%20Now%20Assist%20product%2C%20a%20flagship%20AI%20offering%2C%20surpassed%20%24600%20million%20in%20annual%20contract%20value%20(ACV)%20in%202025%20and%20has%20exceeded%20%24750%20million%20as%20of%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202026.%20The%20company%20expects%20that%20figure%20to%20top%20%241.5%20billion%20by%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%20and%20account%20for%20more%20than%2030%25%20of%20total%20ACV%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20suggests%20AI%20is%20increasingly%20embedded%20in%20larger%20ServiceNow%20deals.%20In%202025%2C%2091%25%20of%20net%20new%20ACV%20came%20from%20customers%20buying%20five%20or%20more%20products%2C%20with%20a%20sharp%20increase%20in%20multi-product%20deals%20that%20include%20Now%20Assist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EServiceNow%20also%20uses%20its%20own%20operations%20as%20proof%20of%20concept.%20Its%20internal%20AI%20deployment%20generated%20%24500%20million%20in%20annualized%20value%20in%202025%2C%20including%20%24100%20million%20in%20operating%20expense%20savings.%20Those%20savings%20are%20expected%20to%20accelerate%20to%20more%20than%20%24200%20million%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.b