the%20new%20coal%2C%26quot%3B%20Sankar%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BAIP%20is%20the%20train.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pointed%20to%20Jevons%20paradox%2C%20the%20idea%20that%20gains%20in%20efficiency%20increase%20overall%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20Victorians%20built%20more%20efficient%20steam%20engines%2C%20everyone%20assumed%20coal%20consumption%20would%20fall.%20Instead%2C%20it%20skyrocketed%2C%26quot%3B%20Sankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalantir%2C%20which%20builds%20bespoke%20software%20and%20AI%20systems%20for%20government%20and%20business%20clients%2C%20posted%20strong%20first-quarter%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20US%20revenue%20doubled%20year%20over%20year%20to%20%241.28%20billion%2C%20while%20total%20revenue%20jumped%2085%25%20to%20%241.6%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Palantir%20is%20trying%20to%20strike%20a%20balance.%20Sankar%20repeatedly%20said%20that%20Palantir%20stands%20against%20AI%20slop%20by%20calling%20itself%20a%20%26quot%3Bno%20slop%20zone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20blindly%20burning%20through%20tokens%20%E2%80%94%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-tokenmaxxing-token-quotas-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20developers%20call%20tokenmaxxing%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20Palantir%20says%20it%20focuses%20on%20ensuring%20its%20AI%20delivers%20real%20value%2C%20rather%20than%20spinning%20up%20dazzling%20demos%20that%20go%20nowhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20tokens%20means%20more%20slop%2C%26quot%3B%20Sankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantir-q1-2026-earnings-cto-ai-tokens-coal-tech-boom-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777934136000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f90c9b38bee05c96983abe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bu