%20Business%20Insider.%20Photos%20of%20Bezos%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-tech-billionaires-zuckerberg-bezos-high-fashion-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20at%20recent%20fashion%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20sparked%20a%20similar%20reaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20also%20been%2013%2C000%20posts%20on%20X%20calling%20for%20a%20boycott%20of%20the%20event%20because%20of%20the%20Bezos'%20involvement%2C%20PeakMetrics%20found%2C%20namely%20by%20not%20tuning%20into%20coverage%20or%20purchasing%20Vogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos%2C%20who%20skipped%20Monday's%20red%20carpet%2C%20and%20S%C3%A1nchez%20Bezos%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20backlash%20is%20largely%20targeting%20the%20Bezoses.%20Other%20billionaires%20involved%20in%20the%20event%2C%20including%20cochair%20Beyonc%C3%A9%2C%20have%20not%20received%20the%20same%20level%20of%20pushback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20Everyone%20Hates%20Elon%2C%20which%20also%20organized%20a%20protest%20in%20Venice%20around%20Bezos%20and%20S%C3%A1nchez%20Bezos'%20wedding%2C%20launched%20its%20initiative%20%26quot%3Bruin%26quot%3B%20the%20Met%20Gala%20for%20Bezos%20and%20%26quot%3BTrump's%20Billionaires%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20raised%20more%20than%20%2422%2C000.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20Amazon%20worker%20video%2C%20they%20plastered%20posters%20around%20the%20city%2C%20hid%20hundreds%20of%20small%20bottles%20filled%20with%20yellow%20liquid%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nod%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-delivery-drivers-say-they-speed-urinate-in-bottles-2018-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20said%20they%20urinate%20in%20bottles%20%E2%80%94%20inside%20the%20museum%2C%20and%20installed%20empty%20plastic%20bottles%20outside%20the%20building%20with%20a%20sign%20reading%2C%20%26quot%3Bgood%20enough%20for%20his%20staff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20a%20group%20of%20Amazon%20workers%20put%20on%20a%20fashion%20show%2C%20called%20the%20%26quot%3BBall%20Without%20Billionaires%2C%26quot%3B%20on%20Monday%20afternoon%20as%20Met%20Gala%20counterprogramming%2C%20and%20protesters%20gathered%20near%20the%20event%2C%20holding%20signs%20lambasting%20billionaires%20and%20letters%20spelling%20%26quot%3Btax%20the%20rich.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Protesters%20gathered%20near%20the%20Met%20Gala%20to%20protest%20billionaires%20amid%20growing%20scrutiny%20of%20the%20ultrawealthy.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f9265b38bee05c96983baf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EProtesters%20gathered%20near%20the%20Met%20Gala%20to%20protest%20billionaires%20amid%20growing%20scrutiny%20of%20the%20ultrawealthy.%3Cp%3ESpencer%20Platt%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20criticism%20is%20also%20coming%20from%20inside%20the%20fashion%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELivia%20Giuggioli%20Firth%2C%20a%20sustainable%20fashion%20advocate%20who%20has%20attended%2010%20Met%20Galas%2C%20posted%20an%20Instagram%20video%20directed%20at%20Wintour%2C%20criticizing%20her%20for%20bringing%20Bezos%20and%20S%C3%A1nchez%20Bezos%20into%20the%20fold%20and%20describing%20him%20as%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20unethical%20people%20in%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20chose%20to%20side%20on%20this%20line%20of%20history%2C%20which%20says%20the%20empire%20is%20really%20strong%2C%20and%20alive%2C%20and%20kicking%2C%20and%20tonight%20you%20will%20see%20the%20biggest%20manifestation%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20the%20video%2C%20referring%20to%20Bezos%20and%20his%20support%20of%20Trump.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20Hunger%20Games%20scenes.%20They%20wear%20costumes%20there%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EActor%20Taraji%20P.%20Henson%2C%20who%20has%20attended%20the%20eve