aid%20he%20has%20%24471%20million%20in%20shares%20of%20Stripe%2C%20where%20he%20served%20as%20chief%20technology%20officer%20before%20becoming%20an%20executive%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20among%20other%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dd22fe09-8b4b-440a-aeec-e46b715af926%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrockman%20said%20he'd%20donate%20%24100%2C000%20to%20OpenAI's%20charity%20%E2%80%94%20but%20didn't%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBrockman's%20testimony%20kicked%20off%20with%20an%20email%20he%20sent%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyahoo-marissa-mayer-rise-and-fall-2017-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMarissa%20Mayer%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20in%202014%20when%20she%20was%20still%20CEO%20of%20Yahoo.%20In%20it%2C%20he%20told%20her%20about%20the%20AI%20lab%20he%20was%20starting%20with%20donations%20from%20Silicon%20Valley%20bigwigs%20like%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20Reid%20Hoffman%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPeter%20Thiel.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrockman%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bpersonally%20donating%26quot%3B%20%24100%2C000%2C%20it%20emerged%20in%20court%20on%20Monday.%20Brockman%20made%20the%20same%20claim%20to%20other%20potential%20donors%2C%20but%20never%20came%20through%20with%20the%20money%2C%20he%20acknowledged%20under%20questioning%20by%20Musk's%20lawyer%20Steven%20Molo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20explaining%20the%20delay%2C%20Brockman%20put%20the%20onus%20on%20Altman%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20asked%20Sam%20when%20I%20should%20donate%20this%2C%20and%20he%20said%20he%20would%20let%20me%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f033a1c-895a-44c3-af3f-9ba135ba925b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrockman%20confirms%20OpenAI%20is%20exploring%20a%20public%20offering%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20testimony%2C%20Brockman%20confirmed%20publicly%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20OpenAI%20was%20exploring%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-openai-ipo-cfo-sarah-friar-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIPO%20for%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20exploring%20the%20possibility%20of%20doing%20something%20called%20an%20initial%20public%20offering%2C%20is%20that%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20Molo%20asked%20Brockman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Brockman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20exploring%20it%2C%20aren't%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20Molo%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20Brockman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20OpenAI%20were%20to%20go%20public%2C%20its%20initial%20public%20offering%20would%20be%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20record%20for%20the%20biggest%20IPO%20is%20Saudi%20Aramco%2C%20in%202019%2C%20at%20about%20%2429%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20most%20recent%20round%20of%20fundraising%20put%20its%20private%20valuation%20at%20about%20%24850%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20and%20SpaceX%20are%20also%20reportedly%20considering%20IPOs%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222993f9a5-f947-4b41-a7b9-f62156b5f4af%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%20asked%20Greg%20Brockman%20to%20settle%20the%20lawsuit%202%20days%20before%20the%20trial%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20before%20court%20opened%20for%20the%20day%2C%20lawyers%20for%20the%20OpenAI%20defendants%20revealed%20in%20a%20court%20filing%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-open-ai-trial-offered-settlement-to-brockman-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMusk%20reached%20out%20to%20Brockman%3C%2Fa%3E%20two%20days%20before%20the%20trial%20began%20to%20gauge%20his%20interest%20in%20a%20settlement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrockman%20suggested%20that%20both%20sides%20drop%20all%20their%20claims.%20Musk%20didn't%20appear%20satisfied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20the%20end%20of%20this%20week%2C%20you%20and%20Sam%20will%20be%20the%20most%20hated%20men%20in%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20responded%2C%20according%20to%20the%20filing.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20insist%2C%20so%20it%20will%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyers%20for%20Brockman%2C%20Altman%2C%20and%20OpenAI%20asked%20US%20District%20Judge%20Yvonne%20Gonzalez%20Rogers%20to%20allow%20the%20communications%20to%20be%20entered%20into%20evidence.%20She%20hasn't%20ruled%20on%20whether%20the%20jury%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20see%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6f15022-9a49-4ce9-b647-27787796ad63%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EElon%20Musk's%20very%20expensive%20expert%20witness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20witness%20to%20testify%20on%20Monday%20was%20Stuart%20Russell%2C%20an%20artificial%20intelligence%20expert%20who%20teaches%20computer%20science%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20memorable%20part%20of%20Russell's%20testimony%20was%20when%20he%20talked%20about%20how%20much%20Musk's%20legal%20team%20paid%20him.%20He%20received%20an%20eye-popping%20%245%2C000%20per%20hour%20for%2040%20hours%20of%20preparatory%20work.%20Expert%20witnesses%20in%20high-profile%20cases%20typically%20make%20between%20%24500%20to%20%241%2C000%20per%20hour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussell%20testified%20he%20was%20making%20%24235%2C000%20altogether%20from%20his%20work%20on%20the%20trial%2C%20which%20he%20said%20amounts%20to%20about%2020%25%20of%20his%20income%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20being%20paid%20by%20Excession%2C%20which%20is%20Musk's%20family%20office%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-you-missed-greg-brockman-testimony-openai-trial-elon-musk-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777932102000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f9029cb3045b292f63697c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-yo