n-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Codex%20to%20all%20corporate%20employees%2C%20pushing%20beyond%20its%20in-house%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-kiro-project-ai-agents-software-coding-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKiro%3C%2Fa%3E%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20to%20staff%2C%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20VP%20of%20Amazon%20Software%20Builder%20Experience%20Jim%20Haughwout%20said%20Claude%20Code%20would%20be%20available%20company-wide%20immediately%2C%20with%20OpenAI's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-openai-codex-used-adobe-lightroom-like-human-only-faster-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECodex%3C%2Fa%3E%20set%20to%20follow%20on%20May%2012.%20Both%20tools%20will%20run%20on%20Amazon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ai-capacity-crunch-pushed-customers-to-rivals-google-anthropic-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBedrock%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20be%20managed%20through%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%2C%20saving%20the%20need%20to%20set%20up%20infrastructure%20or%20manage%20capacity%2C%20the%20note%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20help%20you%20invent%20more%20for%20customers%2C%20we%20are%20expanding%20the%20agentic%20Al%20tools%20available%20to%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20Haughwout%20said%20in%20the%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20significantly%20broadens%20Amazon's%20use%20of%20outside%20AI%20coding%20tools.%20Until%20recently%2C%20Claude%20Code%20wasn't%20formally%20approved%20for%20production%20use%2C%20forcing%20employees%20to%20seek%20special%20clearance.%20That%20restriction%20had%20fueled%20complaints%20from%20engineers%20who%20preferred%20it%20over%20AWS's%20in-house%20Kiro%20tool%2C%20Business%20Insider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-engineers-grate-against-internal-limits-claude-code-kiro-ai-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rollout%20also%20reflects%20Amazon's%20deepening%20partnerships%20with%20leading%20AI%20labs%2C%20including%20Anthropic%20and%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20company%20is%20now%20%26quot%3Bstandardizing%26quot%3B%20access%20to%20Claude%20Code%20and%20Codex%2C%20eliminating%20the%20need%20for%20separate%20approvals%20to%20officially%20use%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Amazon%2C%20we've%20long%20held%20there's%20no%20one-size-fits-all%20approach%20to%20how%20our%20teams%20innovate%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20builders%20are%20using%20Kiro%20for%20agentic%20coding%2C%20and%20now%20with%20both%20Claude%20Code%20and%20Codex%20running%20on%20AWS%2C%20we%20are%20making%20additional%20tools%20available%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22439ef15d-6b7c-46ac-92a9-a1a6b7009d7d%5C%22%3EFrom%20resistance%20to%20rollout%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20engineers%20had%20been%20vocal%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20Claude%20Code%20for%20production%20work%2C%20particularly%20as%20competing%20tools%20gained%20traction.%20The%20restrictions%20became%20a%20point%20of%20friction%20inside%20the%20company%2C%20with%20some%20employees%20arguing%20that%20Amazon%20risked%20falling%20behind%20in%20developer%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20company%20is%20scaling%20both%20Claude%20Code%20and%20Codex%20across%20its%20corporate%20workforce%2C%20a%20sign%20that%20leadership%20views%20AI%20coding%20assistants%20as%20essential%20infrastructure%20rather%20than%20optional%20add-ons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20running%20Claude%20Code%20and%20Codex%20through%20Bedrock%2C%20Amazon%20can%20keep%20usage%20within%20its%20own%20cloud%20environment%2C%20maintaining%20tighter%20control%20over%20data%20security%20and%20compliance%20while%20still%20giving%20employees%20access%20to%20cutting-edge%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20run%20on%20Bedrock%2C%20where%20all%20inference%20runs%2C%26quot%3B%20Haighwout%20said%20in%20the%20note.%20%26quot%3BBoth%20will%20have%20easy%20install%20for%20all%20Amazon%20builders.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20internal%20teams%20are%20still%20%26quot%3Bprimarily%20using%26quot%3B%20Kiro%2C%20which%20has%20been%20adopted%20by%2083%25%20of%20the%20company's%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20has%20invested%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20both%20Anthropic%20and%20OpenAI%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Amazon%20announced%20a%20major%20new%20partnership%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-openai-deal-cloud-ai-race-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20investing%20up%20to%20%2450%20billion%20in%20the%20AI%20company.%20In%20exchange%2C%20OpenAI%20agreed%20to%20use%20Amazon's%20Trainium%20chips%20and%20work%20with%20AWS%20on%20customized%20models%20and%20a%20new%20AI%20agent%20service%20built%20on%20Amazon's%20cloud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Amazon%20has%20doubled%20down%20on%20its%20relationship%20with%20Anthropic.%20In%20April%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20would%20invest%20up%20to%20an%20additional%20%2425%20billion%20in%20the%20startup%2C%20on%20top%20of%20the%20%248%20billion%20it%20had%20already%20pledged.%20Anthropic%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20committed%20to%20buying%20%24100%20billion%20worth%20of%20Trainium%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aekim%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eekim%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%2C%20Telegram%2C%20or%20WhatsApp%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A650-942-306