%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexperts-think-ai-bring-next-industrial-revolution-trigger-nuclear-war-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIndustrial%20Revolution-sized%20paradigm%20shift%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20who%20do%20business%20leaders%20call%20when%20they%20need%20to%20make%20a%20change%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConsultants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20is%20teaming%20up%20with%20some%20of%20Wall%20Street's%20biggest%20investors%20for%20a%20%241.5%20billion%20joint%20venture%20for%20%26quot%3BAI-native%20enterprise%20services%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20in%20easier-to-understand%20terms%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-ai-adoption-return-on-investment-analysis-enterprise-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BMcKinsey%20of%20AI%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20one%20insider%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20founding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-trillion-dollar-valuation-on-secondary-markets-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epartners%2C%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Blackstone%2C%20Hellman%20%26amp%3B%20Friedman%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-names-7-management-committee-asset-wealth-management-gsam-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs'%20asset%20management%20arm%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20announced%20the%20deal%20Monday.%20The%20first%20three%20firms%20each%20contributed%20%24300%20million%20to%20the%20deal%2C%20while%20Goldman%20contributed%20%24150%20million%2C%20according%20to%20the%20person%20familiar.%20The%20remaining%20funding%20comes%20from%20a%20consortium%20of%20major%20investors%2C%20including%20Apollo%2C%20General%20Atlantic%2C%20Leonard%20Green%2C%20GIC%2C%20and%20Sequoia%20Capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20rare%20convergence%3A%20massive%20market%20need%2C%20the%20unmatched%20AI%20technical%20capability%20of%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-longtime-rivals-partnering-apollo-blackstone-anthropic-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsortium%20of%20investors%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20reach%20to%20scale%20fast%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hellman%20%26amp%3B%20Friedman%20CEO%20Patrick%20Healy%20in%20a%20media%20release%20accompanying%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unnamed%20AI%20firm%20is%20a%20way%20for%20its%20backers%20to%20drive%20returns%20across%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fportfolio-operations-jobs-rising-stars-of-private-equity-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etheir%20portfolio%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20create%20a%20playbook%20for%20transformation%20through%20the%20tech%2C%20and%20ultimately%20justify%20the%20billions%20these%20firms%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fportfolio-operations-jobs-rising-stars-of-private-equity-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epouring%20into%20AI%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20got%20275%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20Jon%20Gray%2C%20Blackstone's%20president%2C%20said%20on%20CNBC%20on%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20very%20interested%20in%20using%20Anthropic's%20enterprise%20technology%2C%20but%20they're%20saying%2C%20'Can%20you%20help%20me%20get%20there%3F%20Can%20you%20help%20me%20change%20the%20workflow%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20investors%20like%20Gray%2C%20helping%20them%20out%20isn't%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20altruism%3B%20it%20could%20materially%20affect%20their%20bottom%20lines.%20Labor%20is%20a%20%2460%20trillion%20annual%20cost%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20make%20people%2015%25%20more%20efficient%2C%20that's%20%249%20trillion.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrivate%20equity%20firms%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-equity-slowdown-careers-impact-private-credit-portfolio-operations-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunder%20pressure%20to%20generate%20returns%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20holding%20periods%20have%20been%20stretching.%20Almost%2040%25%20of%20companies%20are%20now%20held%20for%20more%20than%205%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bain.com%2Finsights%2Foutlook-gaining-traction-global-private-equity-report-2026%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Bain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20up%20from%2029%25%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20demand%20is%20off%20the%20charts%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brian%20Mulberry%2C%20chief%20market%20strategist%20at%20Zacks%20Portfolio%20Management%2C%20who%20sees%20the%20venture%20as%20the%20convergence%20of%20several%20forces%3A%20growing%20computing%20power%20as%20data%20centers%20multiply%2C%20the%20urgency%20for%20financial%20sponsors%20to%20offload%20aging%20assets%2C%20and%20the%20soaring%20costs%20affiliated%20with%20rapid%20token%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20computing%20power%20grows%2C%20more%20data%20centers%20come%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20use%20of%20this%20AI%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20try%20and%20drive%20productivity%20then%20becomes%20very%20scalable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228bd9094f-f81a-4b38-86df-9a153546c857%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%20growing%20foothold%20on%20Wall%20Street%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20central%20part%20of%20the%20venture%20will%20involve%20working%20closely%20with%20Anthropic'%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhottest-job-ai-forward-deployed-engineer-skills-need-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Es%20engineers%20to%20embed%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20their%20workflows%20and%20reshape%20internal%20processes.%20In%20practice%2C%20that%20could%20include%20introducing%20AI-driven%20agents%20into%20existing%20systems%2C%20allowing%20companies%20to%20complete%20tasks%20faster%2C%20according%20to%20a%20second%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20deal's%20logistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20advantage%20for%20the%20venture's%20clients%20will%20be%20access%20to%20the%20latest%20upgrades%20to%20Anthropic's%20models%2C%20said%20another%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20deal's%20logistics%2C%20adding%20that%20preemptive%20access%20to%20these%20models%20before%20the%20public%20receives%20them%20could%20help%20them%20address%20mounting%20cybersecurity%20concerns%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20which%20are%20tied%20to%20the%20unprecedented%20capabilities%20of%20Anthropic's%20own%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20weeks%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-mythos-ai-cybersecurity-financial-system-risks-retail-investor-data-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic's%20Mythos%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20advanced%20LLM%20that%20has%20stoked%20concerns%20among%20US%20officials%2C%20has%20been%20a%20fixation%20for%20banks%20and%20large%20corporations%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eare%20trying%20to%20secure%20themselves%20against%20its%20unprecedented%20cyber%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a82f2941-a669-455b-ba03-91f660a0aec7%5C%22%3EBillions%20on%20the%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20new%20venture%20can%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20bring%20businesses%20into%20the%20AI%20era%2C%20it%20will%20likely%20be%20a%20very%20valuable%20company%3A%20Blackstone's%20own%20portfolio%20companies'%20spending%20on%20large%20language%20models%20is%20up%2015%20times%20in%20the%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20rising%20tide%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Thomas%20T.%20Thomas%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20private-equity%20AI%20value%20creation%20firm%20Teragonia.%20His%20firm%20has%20built%20a%20software%20platform%20for%20middle-market%20private%20equity%20firms%20to%20apply%20AI%20insights%20to%20their%20businesses%2C%20targeting%20a%20market%20that%20owns%20trillions%20of%20dollars%20in%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20a%20big%20market%20to%20serve%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20a%20hard%20one%2C%20Thomas%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20challenge%20of%20transforming%20businesses%20holistically%20within%20the%20timeframe%20of%20a%20private%20equity%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20companies%20do%20need%20to%20exit%2C%20or%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20liquidity%20event%20in%20about%2060%20months%2C%20or%20faster%20if%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BDoing%20that%20and%20telling%20an%20AI%20value%20creation%20story%20in%20a%20cohesive%20fashion%20is%20another%20matter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20longer-term%20payoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlackstone%20says%20it%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20data%20center%20investor%2C%20with%20over%20%24150%20billion%20in%20data%20centers%20globally%20and%20a%20%24160%20billion%20pipeline%20of%20potential%20deals.%20The%20four%20biggest%20players%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Google%2C%20have%20planned%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-earnings-microsoft-ai-investment-capex-plan-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20%24725%20billion%20in%20spendin%3C%2Fa%3Eg%20this%20year%2C%20which%20has%20some%20worried%20about%20the%20sheer%20size%20of%20the%20bet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrivate%20equity%20has%20long%20influenced%20corporate%20strategy%2C%20first%20by%20breaking%20up%20the%20midcentury%20corporate%20conglomerates%20into%20focused%20businesses%20and%20then%20by%20running%20companies%20with%20a%20ruthless%20focus%20toward%20driving%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20sector%20can%20create%20a%20repeatable%20playbook%20for%20artificial%20intelligence%20transformation%2C%20its%20data%20center%20bets%20are%20likely%20to%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstone-anthropic-hellman-goldman-sachs-ai-joint-venture-consulting-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777927856000%2C%