questions%2C%20drawing%20laughter%20and%20exasperated%20sighs%20from%20the%20co-hosts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20other%20times%2C%20he%20seemed%20to%20have%20a%20bone%20to%20pick%20with%20the%20network%2C%20telling%20the%20hosts%20multiple%20times%20that%20CNBC%20had%20previously%20predicted%20GameStop%20would%20do%20%26quot%3Breally%2C%20really%20poorly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20four%20different%20CNBC%20hosts%20took%20their%20turns%20asking%20questions%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20after%20hitting%20a%20wall%2C%20gave%20deep%20exhales%20and%20perplexed%20looks%20to%20his%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20don't%20have%20time%20to%20watch%20the%20interview%2C%20or%20who%20are%20left%20even%20more%20confused%20after%20finishing%20it%2C%20we%20captured%20the%20most%20important%20frames.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECohen%20looks%20distracted%20out%20of%20the%20gate%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222788%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ryan%20Cohen%20during%20his%20CNBC%20interview%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8ee9b38bee05c96983914%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221106%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGameStop%20CEO%20Ryan%20Cohen%20in%20the%20opening%20seconds%20of%20his%20CNBC%20interview%3Cp%3ECNBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fairness%20to%20Cohen%2C%20it's%20an%20early-morning%20CNBC%20show.%20We%20don't%20know%20what%20time%20zone%20the%20GameStop%20CEO%20was%20recording%20from%2C%20which%20could%20make%20it%20even%20earlier%20for%20him.%20But%20regardless%20%E2%80%94%20the%20guy%20looks%20tired%20from%20the%20get-go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20initial%20greeting%2C%20the%20GameStop%20CEO's%20eyes%20begin%20to%20wander%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20not%20clear%20if%20he's%20simply%20reading%20something%20on%20screen%20or%20focusing%20on%20something%20else%2C%20but%20he's%20definitely%20not%20focusing%20on%20the%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20rationale%20for%20wanting%20to%20pursue%20a%20deal%20like%20this%2C%20Cohen's%20facial%20expressions%20flit%20between%20a%20couple%20of%20reactions%20in%20rapid%20succession%2C%20eyebrow%20arching%20almost%20comically%2C%20before%20he%20answers%20while%20looking%20up%20and%20away%20from%20the%20camera.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECohen's%20hanging%20%26quot%3Bno%26quot%3B%20leads%20to%20a%20smile%20and%20chuckle-exhale%20from%20Andrew%20Ross%20Sorkin.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Andrew%20Ross%20Sorkin%20grins%20at%20GameStop%20CEO%20Ryan%20Cohen's%20answer.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8fe4338bee05c969839e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221110%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndrew%20Ross%20Sorkin%20grins%20at%20GameStop%20CEO%20Ryan%20Cohen's%20answer.%3Cp%3ECNBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-bubble-andrew-ross-sorkin-1929-crash-book-ai-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAndrew%20Ross%20Sorkin%3C%2Fa%3E%20asks%20for%20the%20details%20of%20GameStop's%20proposal%3A%20%26quot%3BYou've%20had%20conversations%20with%20the%20company%3F%20You've%20tried%3F%20What's%20happened%20here%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20answers%20with%20a%20flat%20%26quot%3BNo%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20brief%20pause%20that%20hangs%20in%20the%20air%20until%20Sorkin%20looks%20down%2C%20smiling%2C%20and%20lets%20out%20a%20soft%20laugh-exhale%20as%20Cohen%20picks%20back%20up%20with%3A%20%26quot%3BWe're%20just%20starting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESorkin%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20does%20the%20math%20math%3F%26quot%3B%20Cohen's%20%26quot%3Bwe'll%20see%20what%20happens%26quot%3B%20draws%20another%20chuckle.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221136%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screengrab%20from%20CNBC's%20interview%20with%20GameStop%20CEO%20Ryan%20Cohen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8f1f7b3045b292f6368ad%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221134%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECNBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESorkin%20asks%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20for%20an%20explanation%20of%20the%20math%20behind%20the%20proposal.%20How%20exactly%20does%20GameStop%20plan%20to%20pay%20for%20eBay%2C%20as%20there%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20roughly%20%2416%20billion%20gap%20in%20proposed%20financing%20and%20the%20deal%20price%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20shifts%20his%20eyes%20to%20the%20side%20before%20looking%20down.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20on%20our%20website%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20half%20cash%2C%20half%20stock.%26quot%3B%20(Variations%20of%20%26quot%3Bit's%20on%20our%20website%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bit's%20half%20cash%2C%20half%20stock%26quot%3B%20are%20repeated%20often%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20interview.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESorkin%20notes%20that%20he's%20read%20the%20website%20but%20many%20viewers%20haven't%20%E2%80%94%20can%20he%20walk%20them%20through%20it%3F%20Cohen%20asks%20%26quot%3Bwhich%20part.%26quot%3B%20Sorkin%20gives%20another%20detailed%20question%20pointing%20out%20the%20roughly%20%2416%20billion%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20see%20what%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20says%2C%20leading%20to%20another%20short%20laugh-exhale%20from%20Sorkin%20and%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBecky%20Quick%20jumps%20in%20with%20a%20laugh%20and%20raised%20eyebrows%20when%20Cohen%20states%20his%20confusion.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221116%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Becky%20Quick%20leaned%20in%20to%20ask%20Cohen%20about%20where%20GameStop%20would%20find%20the%20money%20for%20eBay.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8f3d6b3045b292f6368c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221114%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQuick%20leaned%20in%20to%20ask%20Cohen%20about%20where%20GameStop%20would%20find%20the%20money%20for%20eBay.%3Cp%3ECNBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20host%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcnbcs-becky-quick-gives-a-piece-of-her-mind-to-sexist-business-owners-2012-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBecky%20Quick%3C%2Fa%3E%20jumps%20in%2C%20cutting%20the%20tension%20between%20Sorkin%20and%20Cohen%20to%20say%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bstraightforward%20question%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20she%20didn't%20%26quot%3Bget%20it.%26quot%3B%20She%20laughs%20a%20bewildered%20laugh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere's%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20money%20coming%20from%3F%20Andrew%20laid%20it%20out%20pretty%20clearly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20referencing%20Sorkin's%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20understand%20your%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20replies%20as%20Quick's%20eyebrows%20shoot%20up.%20He%20repeats%20that%20the%20full%20details%20are%20on%20GameStop's%20websites%20and%20then%20offers%20up%20something%20new%3A%20the%20company%20could%20issue%20new%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuick%20leans%20forward%3A%20%26quot%3BBut%20you're%20on%20our%20air.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20understand%20your%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20repeats%20as%20the%20silence%20hangs%20awkwardly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECohen%20goes%20a%20bit%20on%20the%20offensive%2C%20saying%20CNBC%20called%20for%20%26quot%3BGameStop's%20demise.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221096%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joe%20Kernen%20is%20pictured%20interviewing%20GameStop%20CEO%20Ryan%20Cohen%20on%20CNBC.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8baf93022d9b19bc00215%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221086%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20via%20CNBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20we%20start%20to%20see%20some%20semblance%20of%20moxie%20from%20Cohen%2C%20who%20has%20been%20noticeably%20low%20energy%20for%20the%20interview%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHost%20Michael%20Santoli%20points%20out%20that%20eBay%20has%20long%20been%20a%20public%20company%2C%20while%20GameStop's%20revenue%20is%20down.%20%26quot%3BWhere's%20the%20evidence%20that%20you%20know%20how%20to%20grow%20a%20mature%20consumer%20business%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDidn't%20you%20guys%20call%20for%20GameStop's%20demise%20multiple%20times%3F%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20replies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESantoli%20asks%20if%20Cohen%20is%20saying%20that%20because%20GameStop%20isn't%20%26quot%3Bdead%26quot%3B%20that%20means%20he%20knows%20how%20to%20grow%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20our%20financial%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20says.%20%26quot%3BIs%20it%20better%20than%20you%20guys%20anticipated%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomeone%20off-screen%20can%20be%20heard%20letting%20out%20a%20quick%20laugh%2C%20though%20it's%20not%20clear%20who.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EQuick's%20eyes%20look%20to%20the%20ceiling%20in%20confusion.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221094%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CNBC's%20Becky%20Quick%20looks%20confused%20during%20an%20interview%20with%20GameStop%20CEO%20Ryan%20Cohen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8bc07ab24bc0b23a18fef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22552%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EScreenshot%20via%20CNBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EQuick%20asks%20whether%20GameStop%20shareholders%20would%20see%20meaningful%20gains%20from%20an%20eBay%20acquisition%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20dilution%20of%20their%20stock%20and%20more%20debt%2C%20given%20Cohen's%20proposed%20solution%20of%20issuing%20more%20shares%20to%20make%20up%20the%20roughly%20%2416%20billion%20deal%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECohen%20continues%20to%20look%20away%20from%20the%20camera.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20aligned%20with%20shareholders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuick%20then%20lays%20out%20a%20scenario%20where%20shareholders%20might%20not%20see%20a%20significant%20gain%20from%20the%20acquisition.%20Cohen