inated%20them%20quickly.%20I%20think%20this%20is%20an%20example%20of%20the%20degradation%20of%20their%20capability.%20It%20doesn't%20mean%20it's%20all%20gone%2C%20but%20it's%20highly%20degraded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-helicopters-destroy-iran-backed-houthi-boats-red-sea-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS%20Navy%20helicopters%3C%2Fa%3E%20saw%20similar%20action%20against%20boats%20attacking%20merchant%20vessels%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20in%20December%202023.%20The%20helicopters%2C%20dispatched%20after%20a%20cargo%20vessel%20sent%20out%20a%20distress%20signal%2C%20sank%20three%20of%20four%20hostile%20small%20boats%20that%20CENTCOM%20said%20had%20originated%20from%20Houthi-controlled%20areas%20in%20Yemen.%20The%20Iran-backed%20militants%20employ%20tactics%20similar%20to%20those%20of%20the%20IRGC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223884%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20US%20Apache%20helicopters%20taxi%20on%20tarmac.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8f21238bee05c96983952%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221644%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Apache%20and%20Seahawk%20helicopters%20went%20after%20Iranian%20small%20boats%20in%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20%26quot%3Beliminating%26quot%3B%20all%20six%20boats%2C%20Adm.%20Brad%20Cooper%20said.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20US%20aircraft%20currently%20operating%20in%20and%20around%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20include%20A-10%20Warthog%20attack%20aircraft%2C%20fighter%20jets%20like%20the%20F-15%20Eagle%20and%20F-35%20Lightning%20II%20stealth%20fighter%2C%20refueling%20tankers%20like%20the%20KC-135%20Stratotanker%2C%20and%20reconnaissance%20aircraft%20like%20the%20RC-135.%20The%20Navy%20also%20has%20two%20aircraft%20carrier%20strike%20groups%20and%20a%20Marine%20Expeditionary%20Unit%20in%20the%20area.%20Multiple%20warships%20are%20operating%20in%20the%20Persian%20Gulf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cruise%20missiles%20were%20going%20after%20both%20US%20Navy%20ships%2C%20but%20mostly%20after%20commercial%20shipping%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooper%20shared.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20had%20drone%20launches%20against%20commercial%20ships%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20the%20small%20boats%20were%20all%20going%20against%20commercial%20ships%2C%20and%20all%20were%20sunk%20by%20Apaches%20and%20Seahawk%20helicopters.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20US%20military%20or%20US-flagged%20commercial%20vessels%20were%20hit%20in%20the%20Iranian%20attacks%2C%20the%20latest%20escalation%20in%20a%20simmering%20conflict%3B%20Cooper%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20whether%20the%20ceasefire%20is%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20military%20actions%20come%20as%20the%20US%20has%20launched%20%26quot%3BProject%20Freedom.%26quot%3B%20US%20forces%20are%20guiding%20commercial%20vessels%20that%20have%20been%20stranded%20and%20need%20safe%20transit%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraffic-data-shows-ships-moving-through-the-strait-of-hormuz-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStrait%20of%20Hormuz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20presents%20a%20range%20of%20threats%20to%20shipping%2C%20including%20naval%20mines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECooper%20said%20that%20US%20forces%20have%20cleared%20a%20path%20through%20the%20strait%20and%20established%20a%20defensive%20umbrella%20for%20vessels%20to%20travel%20under.%20American%20forces%20are%20not%20supporting%20individual%20escorts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20admiral%20shared%20limited%20details%20on%20how%20the%20US%20made%20this%20possible.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20will%20say%20is%2C%20over%20the%20past%20several%20weeks%2C%20we've%20used%20low-observable%20capability%20to%20clear%20that%20path%2C%20and%20we%20validated%20that%20in%20multiple%20ways.%20And%20then%20we%20took%20the%20risk%20by%20using%20US-flagged%20ships%20to%20go%20through%20first%2C%20setting%20the%20example%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-apache-seahawk-helicopters-sank-iranian-small-boats-hormuz-strait-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1777926201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8f69238bee05c96983981%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-apache-seahawk-helicopters-sank-iranian-small-boats-hormuz-strait-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20forces%20have%20cleared%20a%20defended%20path%20through%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20for%20vessels%20to%20transit%20the%20waters%20safely%2C%20a%20top%20American%20commander%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jepstein%40businessinsider.com%20(Jake%20Epstein%2CChris%20Panella)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A95%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paramount%20beats%20earnings%20expectations%20for%20Q1%20with%20its%20WBD%20megadeal%20on%20the%20horizon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226635%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David%20Ellison%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8ded738bee05c9698388e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224423%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EParamount%20Skydance%20CEO%20David%20Ellison%20is%20engineering%20a%20deal%20to%20buy%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery.%3Cp%3EGilbert%20Flores%2FVariety%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EParamount%20Skydance%20impressed%20investors%20in%20its%20first-quarter%20earnings%20report.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company's%20earnings%20came%20in%20above%20expectations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EParamount%2B%20added%20about%20700%2C000%20subscribers%20last%20quarter%2C%20its%20first%20with%20live%20UFC%20matches%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20Skydance%20pleased%20investors%20in%20its%20first%20earnings%20report%