ion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParamount's%20TV%20business%20shrank%20about%206%25%20year%20over%20year%20to%20under%20%243.7%20billion%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcable-tv-household-50-percent-decline-brian-wieser-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecord-cutting%20continues%20to%20ravage%3C%2Fa%3E%20media%20companies.%20However%2C%20Paramount%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-sheridan-yellowstone-spinoffs-sequels-other-tv-projects%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estar%20showrunner%20Taylor%20Sheridan's%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BThe%20Madison%26quot%3B%20was%20his%20strongest%20streaming%20debut%20ever%2C%20with%2012.5%20million%20viewers%20in%20its%20first%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20pleased%20with%20the%20trajectory%20of%20our%20business%20as%20we%20continue%20to%20invest%20in%20key%20areas%20of%20growth%2C%20drive%20greater%20efficiency%20across%20the%20enterprise%20and%20position%20the%20company%20for%20long-term%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Ellison%2C%20Paramount's%20CEO%2C%20in%20his%20first-quarter%20shareholder%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224631a283-d4ca-4efe-bf93-686192384590%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUFC%20fights%20lure%20subscribers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%2B%20added%20700%2C000%20subscribers%20last%20quarter%20as%20it%20began%20showing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-ufc-rights-tko-deal-david-ellison-netflix-streaming-wars-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elive%20UFC%20matches%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%20without%20pay-per-view%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20seven-year%2C%20%247.7%20billion%20deal.%20However%2C%20the%20company%20said%20it%20would%20have%20added%201.9%20million%20if%20not%20for%20its%20decision%20to%20exit%20a%20bundle%20internationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reported%20in%20January%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fufc-paramount-plus-million-new-subscribers-leaked-subscriber-figures-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EParamount%2B%20generated%20about%201%20million%20signups%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20day%20of%20its%20first%20UFC%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParamount's%20namesake%20streamer%20now%20has%2079.6%20million%20subscribers%2C%20which%20is%20ahead%20of%20US-only%20Peacock's%2046%20million%20but%20well%20behind%20its%20top%20rivals.%20Disney%20had%20196%20million%20streaming%20customers%20when%20it%20last%20shared%20subscriber%20figures%20in%20September%202025%2C%20while%20Netflix%20said%20it%20had%20325%20million%20customers%20as%20of%20the%20end%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-ellison-paramount-wbd-deal-shareholders-approve-read-the-memo-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBuying%20WBD%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20help%20Paramount's%20flagship%20streamer%20scale%2C%20since%20the%20HBO%20parent%20had%20131.6%20million%20streaming%20customers%20at%20the%20end%20of%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdavid-ellison-paramount-wbd-deal-shareholders-approve-read-the-memo-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EParamount-WBD%20mega-merger%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20faced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-stars-oppose-paramount-warner-bros-discovery-deal-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eopposition%20from%20Hollywood%20stars%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20JJ%20Abrams%20and%20Ben%20Stiller%2C%20still%20needs%20official%20regulatory%20approval%20in%20the%20US%20and%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2268abb75d-a9df-4e64-abc2-8148e79467d5%5C%22%3ETurning%20to%20tech%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEllison%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-skydance-david-ellison-memo-fourth-quarter-earnings-tech-investment-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprioritizing%20technology%20and%20streaming%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20hopes%20of%20re