0and%20the%20historic%20Karnala%20Fort.%20With%20fresh%20air%2C%20natural%20beauty%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20adventure%2C%20Karnala%20makes%20the%20perfect%20destination%20for%20a%20relaxed%20family%20getaway.%20Best%20of%20all%2C%20it%20can%20be%20experienced%20on%20a%20modest%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-day%20trip%20for%20a%20family%20of%20three%20can%20be%20comfortably%20enjoyed%20on%20a%20budget%20of%20Rs%204%2C000%20to%20Rs%205%2C000%2C%20including%20transport%2C%20food%2C%20accommodation%2C%20entry%20tickets%2C%20and%20local%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A494788%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDay%201%3A%20Mumbai%20to%20Panvel%20%E2%80%93%20Gateway%20to%20nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStart%20your%20trip%20by%20boarding%20a%20suburban%20local%20train%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Panvel.%20Trains%20run%20frequently%20and%20cost%20just%20Rs%2015%20to%20Rs%2025%20per%20person.%20The%20journey%20takes%20around%20an%20hour%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20starting%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-01T213822.115_11zon-1756742924.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20