%2Fkarnala-bird-sanctuary%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPicture%20source%3A%20SceneLoc8%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDay%204%3A%20Nature%20and%20local%20exploration%20at%20a%20slower%20pace%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20two%20active%20days%2C%20slow%20things%20down.%20If%20the%20family%20enjoyed%20the%20sanctuary%2C%20revisit%20it%20for%20a%20shorter%20walk%20or%20take%20a%20second%20attempt%20at%20spotting%20birds%20missed%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlternatively%2C%20explore%20other%20local%20attractions%20around%20Panvel.%20Visit%20Ballaleshwar%20Lake%2C%20a%20peaceful%20spot%20for%20an%20afternoon%20walk%20or%20light%20paddle.%20Another%20option%20is%20Bhor%20Ghat%20Viewpoint%2C%20which%20offers%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332196%2Fvidyasagar-hariharan-flamingos-mumbai-thane-creek-conserve-wetlands-wildlife-photography%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epanoramic%20views%20and%20is%20perfect%20for%20photography%20lovers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnjoy%20a%20local%20lunch%20and%20return%20to%20your%20hotel%20for%20some%20downtime.%20In%20the%20evening%2C%20consider%20a%20visit%20to%20a%20nearby%20temple%20or%20small%20garden%20if%20travelling%20with%20elders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDay%205%3A%20Souvenir%20shopping%20and%20return%20to%20Mumbai%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20your%20final%20morning%2C%20explore%20Panvel%20Market%20for%20souvenirs%20such%20as%20local%20spices%2C%20papads%2C%20dried%20snacks%2C%20or%20handmade%20goods.%20Many%20families%20also%20pick%20up%20fresh%20fruit%20or%20jaggery%20as%20gifts%20or%20travel%20snacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoard%20a%20local%20train%20back%20to%20Mumbai%20in%20the%20afternoon%2C%20with%20your%20bags%20a%20little%20fuller%20and%20hearts%20refreshed%20from%20five%20days%20of%20greenery%2C%20light%20trekking